data.description: !!!$4000 Use as you Choose!!! Don't miss this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with an office and a large bonus room! The 2 story entry allows ample natural light. The kitchen has been recently updated with new flooring, countertops and large single basin sink; the kitchen also has a pantry and additional open shelf storage with a gorgeous wood countertop. The primary bedroom is on the first floor and has a private ensuite and large walk-in closet! Upstairs you will find the remaining two bedrooms as well as an office, large bonus room with flex space and a full bathroom. Outside you'll fall in love with the serenity of the backyard. Entertain or relax on your back deck while enjoying the view of mature trees lining your yard. New roof installed in 2022! Call today to schedule a showing!
